# Build verification

When verifying changes in this repo, run the full build (not just compile):

```bash
./gradlew build detekt checkReadme publishToMavenLocal --continue 2>&1 | tail -120
```

# Detekt

The detekt task can auto-fix certain formatting issues (e.g. import order). **Run detekt twice** before attempting to fix a failure manually; the second run may pass after auto-fixes from the first run.

```bash
./gradlew detekt 2>&1; ./gradlew detekt 2>&1
```
